        },
        {
          "username": "N. F.",
          "rating": 5,
          "contributor_id": "112882728768567229971",
          "user_review_count": 97,
          "user_photo_count": 23,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUuzeaTVDzk7B2G2Ueq7_3pLc-JFToCMhsNLz1zbm-rAyAbW1Fm_Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "Hands down the nation\u2019s best for what my family was battling and I wish we had made the very, very long trip out here sooner. Dr. Athanasian, Dr. Tap, all of the nurses and the concierge team were really fabulous. There is a gift shop with good prices, the cafeteria food was healthy/yummy/affordable. Kids under 12 are not allowed in the recovery unit so make alt childcare plans. Obviously I highly recommend this hospital. Also love that the other best oncologists/surgeons in the nation also said this and place was the best.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURMMXQ3bDhnRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x2016bdf87e63c0a9!3m1!1s2@1:CIHM0ogKEICAgIDL1t7l8gE%7C%7C?hl=en",
